overview.en: DOS Network is a scalable layer-2 network that implements Decentralized Oracle Service, providing real-world data and computing power to mainstream blockchains. It connects smart contracts with real-world data and provides verifiable computing power to blockchains, enabling more application scenarios to be landed on blockchains. DOS Network can support a variety of mainstream blockchains, such as Ethereum, EOS, TRON, ThunderCore and etc.
overview.zh: DOS Network是一个实现了去中心化预言机的可扩展的二层网络，旨在为主流区块链提供数据上链服务和计算力。它将区块链智能合约与真实世界的数据和事件连接起来，还为区块链提供可验证的计算能力，从而使更多应用场景能够在区块链上实现。可支持各种主流区块链，如Ethereum、EOS、TRON、ThunderCore等。
